Dict.py README

Commandlist:

/dict on 		Turns on the dictionary
/dict off		Turns off the dictionary
/dict time x	Changes the timeout period to "x" seconds

-----------------------------------------

Usage:

!define <word>	Prints the definition for that given word

-----------------------------------------

Errors (when a definition isn't returned):

"Errors" occur when:
	-No word is listed to be defined
	-A connection to dictionary.com cannot be established
	-No description is found

Errors all take the form: "Sorry, " and then the error.
